{"word":"ἐπιθυμέω","slug":"ἐπιθυμέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιθυμέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:θυμός'><el>θυμός</el></a>\n<p/><i>to set one's heart upon</i> a thing, <i>lust after, long for, covet, desire</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; also <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <i>to desire to</i> do, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to desire, covet</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τὸ ἐπιθυμοῦν τοῦ πλοῦ  ἐπιθυμία</el>, <i>eagerness</i> for it, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}